name: ELECTRIPS VERSE - HAVE A NICE DREAM
description: life must go on, have a nice dream. work as hard as you can but remember you need rest. A cyborg girl with chainsaw hands depicts a human who must do everything in his power to survive. the girl smokes a cigarette as a symbol as loud as our life needs to chilling. I created this visual as a reminder for you to rest and at the same time a visual for your bedtime.
